a2t.text_actual: Instantly watch current TV shows and acclaimed movies. Anywhere. Get access to a selection of content for free - latest and past episodes of popular current TV shows and a selection of content from Hulu Originals, Anime, Kids, Movies and Latino Upgrade to Hulu Plus from the app to get access to the entire Hulu library of current and back seasons of popular TV shows and movies and stream it across all connected devices from the living room to the desktop Key Features for Hulu Plus • Watch current season episodes of popular TV shows such as Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Family Guy and Modern Family • Enjoy popular kids shows including SpongeBob SquarePants, Pokémon, Caillou and many more, ad-free • Catch up on classic series including Lost, Battlestar Galactica and Sabrina, or explore thousands of critically acclaimed movies • Stream your favorite shows on connected devices such as smart TVs, streaming players, gaming consoles and mobile devices • Directly cast and control your viewing experience from your phone or tablet on to your TV with Chromecast, Xbox One, PS3 and PS4 using the in app remote control • Resume watching from where you left off on your TV or another supported device • Add your favorite videos to your queue for instant access and sharing  • Watch over WiFi, 3G, and 4G • Available for $7.99/month with limited advertising Hulu Plus is supported on most Android 4.x phones and tablets. Service available in the United States and territories. Please contact us at  mobilesupport@hulu.com  or 1-888-907-0345 if you are having issues with compatibility of your device. Use of Hulu Plus is subject to the Hulu Plus Terms of Service: hulu.com/terms
